spanish_vowels %>%
  separate(col = label,
           into = c("id", "bs", "vowel"),
           sep = "-"
          ) %>%
  ggplot() +
  aes(x=f2, y=f1, label=vowel, color = vowel) +
  facet_grid(.~bs) +
  geom_text(alpha=0.5) +#geom_point()
  scale_y_reverse() +
  scale_x_reverse()
